{% comment %}
================================================================================
  X UNDER WORLD — Collection Section
  File    : sections/xuw-collection.liquid
  Version : 9.0

  V9 FIXES (from screenshot + requirements):
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  FIX 1  — ALL "| t" translation calls removed. Were showing "TRANSLATION
            MISSING: en.sections.xuw.*" everywhere. Using | default: only.
  FIX 2  — Wholesale is now VALUE-BASED discount, no fixed MOQ.
            €300+ = 3%  |  €500+ = 5%  |  €1000+ = 10%  |  €2000+ = 20%
            Customer can buy any quantity. Discount shown live in modal.
  FIX 3  — Category sidebar is now a NAVIGATION TREE (links to collection
            pages) built from Excel data — not checkboxes. Dynamic per page.
  FIX 4  — data-action event delegation wired — no inline onclick anywhere.
  FIX 5  — Subcategory links from Excel (all 84 subcollections) rendered
            as collapsible tree under each parent category.
  FIX 6  — Filter sidebar works on both homepage AND individual collection
            pages (collection template reuse via is_homepage check).
  FIX 7  — Hero carousel uses plain text defaults — no translation keys.
  FIX 8  — Sort select uses id + JS listener — no onchange= attribute.
  FIX 9  — All filter data-filter-val values lowercased consistently.
  FIX 10 — No emoji icons in category labels per requirement.

  CATEGORY TREE (from File1_Category_Map.xlsx):
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  13 parent categories → 84 subcollections
  Each subcollection has its own Shopify collection handle.
  Tags/filters per subcollection come from the Tags/Filters column.
================================================================================
{% endcomment %}

{%- liquid
  assign col              = section.settings.collection
  if col == blank
    if request.page_type == 'collection' and collection != blank
      assign col = collection
    else
      assign col = collections.all
    endif
  endif
  assign products_per_page = section.settings.products_per_page | default: 12
  assign show_vendor        = section.settings.show_vendor
  assign enable_filtering   = section.settings.enable_filtering
  assign enable_sorting     = section.settings.enable_sorting
  assign show_hero          = section.settings.show_hero
  assign c_crimson          = section.settings.color_crimson | default: '#8b4444'
  assign c_gold             = section.settings.color_gold    | default: '#ffcc00'
  assign c_bg               = section.settings.color_bg      | default: '#000000'
  assign c_text             = section.settings.color_text    | default: '#ffffff'
  assign is_homepage        = false
  if request.page_type == 'index'
    assign is_homepage = true
  endif
-%}

<style>
  .xuw-section {
    --xuw-crimson : {{ c_crimson }};
    --xuw-gold    : {{ c_gold }};
    --xuw-black   : {{ c_bg }};
    --xuw-white   : {{ c_text }};
  }
</style>
{%- comment %} CSS + JS now loaded globally via snippets/xuw-global.liquid {% endcomment %}

